songs.title: Can’t Survive
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Wrong side of the bed, felt like I wanted to die
I woke up on the wrong side of the bed
Yeah yeah yeah yeah yeah yeah

[Chorus]
I woke up on the wrong side of the bed, felt like I wanted to die
And yeah I still remember what you said every word was a lie
But I can't survive
Without you by my side
I can't survive
Without you by my side

[Verse 1]
Lovin you became a instinct nah Ion't gotta try (yeah)
I promise you if you don't love me back it's a suicide (yeah)
Tie the rope, [?] the rope, my neck and pull it, in my heart, now I lay in my grave
Wish you would have saved me

[Chorus]
I woke up on the wrong side of the bed, felt like I wanted to die
And yeah I still remember what you said every word was a lie
But I can't survive
Without you by my side
I can't survive
Without you by my side

[Instrumental Break]

[Chorus]
I woke up on the wrong side of the bed, felt like I wanted to die
And yeah I still remember what you said every word was a lie
But I can't survive
Without you by my side
I can't survive
Without you by my side
